name: Imperial Squad Leader
Lore: 'Captain Mod Terrik, a typical officer of the Desert Sands sandtrooper unit. Fearless and highly motivated. Willing to sacrifice as many troops as necessary.',
Text: 'Adds 1 to forfeit of your other troopers at same site. When moving with a ''squad'' of exactly three other troopers, all four move for 1 Force. Imperial Trooper Guards at same site may move.',
